Package project1

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    Your Agent for solving Raven's Progressive Matrices.
    ProblemSet
    A list of RavensProblems within one set.
    Project1
    The main driver file for Project1.
    RavensAttribute
    A single variable-value pair that describes some element of a RavensObject.
    RavensFigure
    A single figure in a Raven's Progressive Matrix problem, comprised of a name and a list of RavensObjects.
    RavensObject
    A single object in a RavensFigure -- typically, a single shape in a frame, such as a triangle or a circle -- comprised of a list of RavensAttributes.
    RavensProblem
    A single Raven's Progressive Matrix problem, represented by a type (2x1, 2x2, or 3x3), a String name, and a HashMap of figures.
